Peggy Ann Clifford https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peggy_Ann_Clifford 0 Peggy Ann Clifford (23 March 1921 in Poole, Dorset – 26 May 1986) was a plus size English film and television character actress. She was born Peggy Anne Hamley Champion. Her mother's maiden name was Clifford.
